data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home in the heart of Fishers feels MUCH larger than it's listed square footage - with a huge un-finished basement, the possibilities for this charmer are endless. The basement is roughed-in for plumbing. The HVAC is just a baby, only 4 years old. The loft is perfect for working from home or gaming with friends. Don't miss out on the large backyard, either!
